---
import Greeting from '../components/Greeting';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = "风格预览";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <section class="hero-card card-shell">
    <img src="/img.png" class="hero-image" alt="Hero" />
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <h2>四套视觉方案，一键切换</h2>
      <p>你可以快速比较 Token、Matrix、Astro Cactus 和融合款的视觉表现。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grid-panels">
    <article class="card-shell">
      <h3>1. Token 模板风</h3>
      <p>强调通透卡片、柔和渐变与现代产品落地页质感。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card-shell">
      <h3>2. Matrix Astro 风</h3>
      <p>赛博深色基调、霓虹高亮和科技感边框。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card-shell">
      <h3>3. Astro Cactus 风</h3>
      <p>极简排版、阅读优先、低饱和护眼配色。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card-shell">
      <h3>4. Fusion 组合风</h3>
      <p>结合以上三者，适合做默认展示风格。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <Greeting client:load messages={["Hi", "Hello", "Howdy", "Hey there"]} />
</BaseLayout>
